org.apache.juneau.http.entity

Class BasicHttpEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.http.entity.BasicHttpEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.http.HttpEntity
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ByteArrayEntity, FileEntity, InputStreamEntity, ReaderEntity, SerializedEntity, StringEntity

    @BeanIgnore
public class BasicHttpEntity
extends Object
implements org.apache.http.HttpEntity
    A basic HttpEntity implementation with additional features. Provides the following features:
    • Caching.
    • Fluent setters.
    • Fluent assertions.
    • Externally-supplied/dynamic content.
    • Overview > juneau-marshall > HTTP Parts
